WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:07.000
Start at TeachPlay. Students use the catalog, dashboard, and sign-in entry from one consistent learner workspace.

2
00:00:07.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Use the course account sign-in when official progress and certificate records need to persist.

3
00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
Open the credential, review the outcomes, and enter the guided course.

4
00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:38.000
The guided course shows the complete 12-module pathway, with case studies and beginner AI build prompts.

5
00:00:38.000 --> 00:00:52.000
Complete lessons, watch narrated mini-lectures, draft worksheets, and mark progress.

6
00:00:52.000 --> 00:01:06.000
Open the final submission, add context and evidence, then submit the portfolio for review.

7
00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:22.000
After completion, the certificate handoff shows the credential summary and downloadable credential evidence.
